Get all market symbols' metadata

Source: R/get_market_metadata.R
get_market_metadata.Rd

Get all market symbols' metadata

Usage

get_market_metadata(retries = 3)

Arguments

retries

A numeric value to specify the number of retries in case of failure (optional - default 3).

Value

A data.table with metadata

—————

For more information see documentation: KuCoin - get-symbols-list-deprecated

Examples


# get all symbols' most recent metadata
kucoin::get_market_metadata()
